\faauto\ls5\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 "Now all who love their country follow me!" exclaimed Iskander.  So saying, and at the head of five thousand horsemen, Iskander quitted the field at a rapid pace.
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\tx900\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 
