\faauto\ls7\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 "If she live, she is a prisoner in the Seraglio at Adrianople.  You are as good a judge a
s myself of the prospect that awaits your exertions.  It is, without doubt, a difficult adventure, but such, methinks, as a Christian knight should scarcely shun."
