\faauto\ls7\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 "That were scarcely wise, a
nd certainly not just," replied Iskander; "but ransom will be of no avail.  Hunniades has already offered to restore Karam Bey, and all the prisoners of rank, and the chief trophies, and Amurath has refused to listen to any terms.  The truth is, Iduna has
 found favour in the eyes of his son, the young Mahomed."
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\tx900{\*\pn \pnlvlcont\ilvl0\ls0\pnrnot0\pndec }\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 
