\faauto\ls12\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 
The bridge would only permit a single rider to pass abreast.  It was supported by three arches, the centre one of very considerable size, the others small, and rising out of the shallow water on each side.  In many parts 
