\faauto\ls13\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 It was midnight ere the restless Nic\'e6us, more exhausted by his agitating reverie than by his previous exertions, returned into the cavern, and found refuge in sleep from all his disquietudes.
