\faauto\ls18\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 
"This is not the first time," remarked Iduna, "that you have reminded me of an obligation, the memory of which is indelibly impressed upon my heart, and for which even the present conversation cannot make me feel less
 grateful.  I can never forget that I owe all that is dear to yourself and your companion."
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\tx900{\*\pn \pnlvlcont\ilvl0\ls0\pnrnot0\pndec }\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 
