\faauto\ls18\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 "Beautiful being!" said the prince, advancing and passionately seizing her hand; "pardon me! pardon me! I am not master of my reason; I am nothing, I am nothing while Iduna hesitates!"
