\faauto\ls19\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 "Away! away!" exclaimed the distracted Iduna, as she endeavoured to fly from him.
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\tx900{\*\pn \pnlvlcont\ilvl0\ls0\pnrnot0\pndec }\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 
