\faauto\ls19\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 "He has kept his word, that cunning leech, better than I expected," said Mahomed, seizing her.
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\tx900{\*\pn \pnlvlcont\ilvl0\ls0\pnrnot0\pndec }\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 
