\faauto\ls19\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 "As well as you deserve, ravisher!" exclaimed a majestic voice.  A tall figure rushed forward from the wood, and dashed back the Turk.
\par }\pard \ql \li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\tx900{\*\pn \pnlvlcont\ilvl0\ls0\pnrnot0\pndec }\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\f1\cgrid0 
